{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "There\u2019s one real bug underneath the missing-dependency noise: the new DTO module imported database enums directly, which creates a circular import during SQLAlchemy model initialization. I\u2019m collapsing those DTO fields to plain string wi...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_54", "text": "There\u2019s one real bug underneath the missing-dependency noise: the new DTO module imported database enums directly, which creates a circular import during SQLAlchemy model initialization. I\u2019m collapsing those DTO fields to plain string wire types and cleaning the long lines/import ordering so the backend can actually import and run.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 121, "prompt_index": 15, "prompt_name": "14 \u2014 Repository Layer and Session Service", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T23:32:32-07:00"}
